name: Psychsoft Consulting
overview:
Psychsoft Consulting is an Industry recognized technology consulting firm based in Quincy, MA founded in 1987 with a highly educated, trained and experienced staff to help in all your IT needs. Psychsoft Consulting personnel have years of experience in IT implementation, troubleshooting, design and configuration.

Psychsoft Consulting offers expert help and advice in all aspects of Information Technology including networking, server configuration, backup and recovery, network security and computer repair. Among our areas of service are Novell, Microsoft Windows Server, MS Windows, Linux and Unix, firewall and network security, wireless networking, wireless network security, database design and administration, web site design, web server configuration, file server configuration, network design, network administration, network wiring, printer networking and computer troubleshooting and repair.
